I am a regular user of Seasons corn oil Md ordered from Daraz for the 1st time. I was disappointed as Movex courier rider came up with damaged bottle and almost 1/4th of oil quantity has fallen.  I refused to accept it as bottle might have fallen down and  contacted germs.  The rider also recommended to stop ordering such products from Daraz as he has a lot of packages to deliver everyday and find it difficult. I am still waiting for the response as should I get my replacement order in proper Packaging ???? I request you to consider another courier company and also improve packaging so that we always receive items in good condition.
